name: python-socketio
raw_recipe:
{%set name = "python-socketio" %}
{%set version = "1.7.2" %}
{%set compress_type = "tar.gz" %}
{%set hash_type = "sha256" %}
{%set hash_val = "aa612e5d2901c94946c3004b0e58bb9fb08b214afee59ce4aeafcf8df4deb79a" %}
{%set build_num = "0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.{{ compress_type }}
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.{{ compress_type }}
  {{ hash_type }}: {{ hash_val }}

build:
  number: {{ build_num }}
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record=record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools

  run:
    - python
    - six >=1.9.0
    - python-engineio >=1.0.0

test:
  imports:
    - socketio
    - socketio.base_manager
    - socketio.kombu_manager
    - socketio.middleware
    - socketio.namespace
    - socketio.packet
    - socketio.pubsub_manager
    - socketio.redis_manager
    - socketio.server

about:
  home: http://github.com/miguelgrinberg/python-socketio/
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  license_family: MIT
  summary: 'Socket.IO server'
  doc_url: https://python-socketio.readthedocs.io
  dev_url: http://github.com/miguelgrinberg/python-socketio/


extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - pmlandwehr
